title: Vintage Trouble 2016-06-12 Pinkpop Holland
description:
Here is a nice Pinkpop broadcast. Check my account for more Pinkpop broadcasts.

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

Vintage Trouble
Pinkpop, Megaland, Landgraaf, The Netherlands
June 12, 2016
3FM Stage 14:50-15:50

Setlist (as shown on screen during broadcast, corrections are welcome):
01. Intro
02. High Times
03. Blues Hand Me Down
04. Total Strangers
05. Not Alright By Me
06. Doin' What You Were Doin'
07. Pelvis Pusher
08. Nobody Told Me
09. Run Like The River
10. Strike Your Light

After track 9 (at the 50:56 mark, the broadcast was interrupted for about three minutes.
Maybe there was no permission to stream one particular track ... Anyhow, I have cut out the intermission.
